addr="tfmt-000T"
title="Contributor to a tree"><fr:em>contributors</fr:em></fr:link> to a given tree. This is slightly subtle, because if a bibliographic tree is transcluded, we do not want its contributors to be included.</fr:p><fr:pre><![CDATA[\def\query/contributors[x]{
 \open\query
 \union-fam-rel{
  \isect{
   \transclusion-coslice{\x}
